  "texts": [
    "These tools were not specifically built for medical note analysis or image recognition tasks.",
    "Instead, they were designed to possess versatile cognitive abilities to assist users in accomplishing various tasks.",
    "A prompt may be an inquiry or a directive to carry out a particular action.",
    "In addition, prompts are not limited to being sentences in English.",
    "They can be written in several human languages and may include data inputs such as spreadsheets, technical specifications, research papers, and mathematical equations (3)."
  ]
}